"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-news-2024-0726-1461968-olympics-team-ireland\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"The President of the Olympic Federation of Ireland has said Team Ireland are confident that they can surpass their previous record of six medals at this year's Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 60, \"end\": 72, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999820375, \"rank\": 1.7879857558294008e-11, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 177, \"end\": 182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999956777239919, \"rank\": 4.322294655899755e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The President\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 13}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Federation\", \"from\": 17, \"to\": 39}, {\"ngram\": \"Ireland\", \"from\": 43, \"to\": 50}, {\"ngram\": \"their previous record\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 130}, {\"ngram\": \"six medals\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 144}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Olympic Games\", \"from\": 148, \"to\": 173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking on RT\\u00c9's Morning Ireland, Sarah Keane said they are going to the games with not just their biggest team, but their \\\"best prepared\\\" team.\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 197, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9835396432123026, \"rank\": 0.013767790549921992, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 203, \"end\": 218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morning_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Morning Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q1555508\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morning_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morning_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 220, \"end\": 231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Keane\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah Keane\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Keane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Keane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 264}, {\"ngram\": \"not just their biggest team\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"their \\\"best prepared\\\" team\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One of the important things is that it's a team across a lot of different breadth of sports, whereas traditionally obviously we have medalled in a couple of particular sports such as boxing and rowing and obviously they are very good contenders here again.\\\"\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the important things\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 360}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 393}, {\"ngram\": \"different breadth\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"particular sports\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"rowing\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"very good contenders\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Six [medals] has been our best and we are definitely aiming to be higher than that,\\\" she said, adding that in order to do so, \\\"you have to create double the number of opportunities to medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Six [medals\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"double the number\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"opportunities\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, if you want to get let us say eight medals, you need about 16 opportunities to medal across those sports to really see if it can happen for you.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"eight medals\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"about 16 opportunities\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"those sports\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are very confident that we have those opportunities.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those opportunities\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are going to going to need our team to perform at their best at the time that counts.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our team\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And obviously we will also need a bit of the luck of the Irish as well because that's sport for you.\\\"\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"the luck\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ms Keane said that in the last few years they have worked closely with Sport Ireland towards this year's event, and that an increase in government funding has made a \\\"big difference\\\".\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sport Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ms Keane\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few years\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's event\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"an increase\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"government funding\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"big difference\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a direct link between and direct correlation between funding and high-performance results,\\\" Ms Keane said.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a direct link\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"direct correlation\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"funding\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"high-performance results\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms Keane\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The excitement in Paris \\\"is something else\\\" ahead of the opening ceremony tonight, she said, adding that Team Ireland has \\\"a very prominent place\\\" in the Olympic village.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1507, \"end\": 1512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999956777239919, \"rank\": 4.322294655899755e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999820375, \"rank\": 1.7879857558294008e-11, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The excitement\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"a very prominent place\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic village\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are very close to food.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are very close to transport, very close to anything they need to get to and I think they feel a bit more important because we are in a kind of a prominent place, we are not far from the French team.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1878, \"end\": 1884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9897667403174, \"rank\": 0.01015321035344136, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1743}, {\"ngram\": \"a kind\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1831}, {\"ngram\": \"a prominent place\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I think that's an important part of the belief, important part of us believing that we deserve to be there, we are confident to be there and we are going to perform on this world stage.\\\"\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an important part\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"the belief\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"important part\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"this world stage\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said that many of the roads in Paris are closed down but \\\"they are very organised and the excitement level is something else.\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2119, \"end\": 2124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999956777239919, \"rank\": 4.322294655899755e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the roads\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"the excitement level\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike the last Olympics in Tokyo, which was impacted by the global pandemic, families of the athletes are able to attend the Games.\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2243, \"end\": 2248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998850004860893, \"rank\": 0.00011134163280852589, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last Olympics\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2239}, {\"ngram\": \"the global pandemic\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"families\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are just really excited to be part of this experience,\\\" Ms Keane said, as a lot of families and supporters could not get to Tokyo.\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2479, \"end\": 2484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9998850004860893, \"rank\": 0.00011134163280852589, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_